---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Notice - IPPriv"
  description="Legal notice for IPPriv, operated by LMF Solutions. Publisher information, hosting details, and intellectual property rights."
  keywords="legal notice, mentions légales, IPPriv legal, LMF Solutions"
  type="article"
>
  <div class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <article class="animate-fade-in">
        <header class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">
            Legal Notice
          </h1>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Last updated: March 2026</p>
        </header>

        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">1. Publisher</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              This website (<strong class="text-foreground">www.ippriv.com</strong>) is published by:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none text-muted-foreground space-y-1 mt-4 ml-0">
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Company:</strong> LMF Solutions</li>
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Legal form:</strong> SASU (Société par Actions Simplifiée Unipersonnelle)</li>
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Share capital:</strong> €1,000</li>
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Registered address:</strong> 60 Rue François 1er, 75008 Paris, France</li>
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">SIRET:</strong> 991 974 130 00015</li>
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@ippriv.com">support@ippriv.com</a></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">2. Publication Director</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              The publication director is <strong class="text-foreground">Brandon Visca</strong>,
              acting in his capacity as President of LMF Solutions.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">3. Hosting</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              This website is hosted by:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none text-muted-foreground space-y-1 mt-4 ml-0">
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Company:</strong> Vercel Inc.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Address:</strong> 440 N Barranca Ave #4133, Covina, CA 91723, United States</li>
              <li><strong class="text-foreground">Website:</strong> <a href="https://vercel.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vercel.com</a></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              All content published on this website — including but not limited to text, graphics,
              logos, icons, and code — is the exclusive property of LMF Solutions or its content
              suppliers and is protected by French and international intellectual property laws.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Any reproduction, distribution, modification, or use of any content, in whole or
              in part, without the prior written consent of LMF Solutions is strictly prohibited.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">5. Personal Data &amp; Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              The collection and processing of personal data on this website are governed by our
              <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, in compliance with the General Data Protection
              Regulation (GDPR) and French data protection law (Loi Informatique et Libertés).
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-4">
              In accordance with applicable law, you have the right to access, rectify, and
              request deletion of your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at
              <a href="mailto:support@ippriv.com">support@ippriv.com</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">6. Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              This website uses Plausible Analytics, a privacy-respecting analytics tool that
              does not use cookies and does not collect personally identifiable information.
              No cookie consent is required for analytics purposes.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-4">
              For more information, please refer to our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              LMF Solutions makes every effort to ensure that the information published on
              this website is accurate and up to date. However, we cannot guarantee the
              completeness or accuracy of the content and shall not be liable for any errors
              or omissions, or for any loss or damage arising from reliance on such information.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-4">
              LMF Solutions reserves the right to modify the content of this website at any
              time and without prior notice.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">8. Applicable Law</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              This legal notice is governed by French law. Any dispute relating to the use
              of this website shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the competent
              courts of Paris, France.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
